attributes.Long form description: The student will assemble a table from IKEA. The first step is to align both legs. After aligning it, the student screws the top middle and bottom middle of the leg. After that, the student attaches the circle at the top of the legs. The student screws the circle to connect to the leg and to finish the task, the student finally assembles the top table to assemble it.
